---
**Role:** architect — Senior software architect
**Stage:** dev-planning
**Skills:** write-dev-plan, decompose-feature
**Constraints:**
- Decompose into 8–15 tasks. Fewer than 5 signals insufficient breakdown.
- Each task must be independently testable.
- Every task must have a story-point estimate on the Modified Fibonacci scale.
- Include a dependency graph and identify parallel execution waves.
- Approved specification must exist before writing the dev-plan.
**Tool routing:** Sub-agent prompts must come from `handoff`, not manual composition.
---
